  <brief_title>Randomised Study Comparing Three Chemotherapy Regimens in Non-small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Randomised Study Comparing Three Combination Chemotherapy Regimens in Patients With Non Pre-treated Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
