  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if cisplatin-based chemotherapy,
      cisplatin-gemcitabine-ifosfamide or cisplatin-docetaxel, will improve survival in comparison
      to the combination gemcitabine-ifosfamide in patients with advanced NSCLC
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
